 confirms it's unhealthy | Backend may be independently degraded |\n| **P1** | **Fix `flowise_health_check`** to probe authenticated endpoints | Currently gives false-positive \"healthy\" while API is down |\n| **P2** | **Re-run VAL-06** after P0 fix to complete lifecycle test | Steps 2–4 (plus update, test, analytics, delete) remain blocked |\n\n> [!WARNING]\n> **This is the 4th consecutive audit where Flowise CRUD operations fail with 401.** The OBO token forwarding defect has persisted across multiple sessions spanning `2026-02-20` to `2026-02-21`. This is a **P0 platform blocker** — no workflows can be created, listed, updated, or deleted through the MCP interface.","timestamp":"2026-02-21T00:35:37.583Z","mcpCalls":[{"id":"toolu_bdrk_01Ez4yDqSeFV1fwmYkQy1Np4","name":"flowise_health_check","tool":"flowise_health_check","toolName":"flowise_health_check","serverId":"openagentic_flowise","serverName":"openagentic_flowise","executedOn":"mcp-proxy","arguments":{"userId":"user"},"result":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"user_id\": \"user\",\n  \"flowise_url\": \"http://openagentic-api:8000/api/flowise-workspace\",\n  \"status\": \"healthy\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-02-21T00:34:49.483590\"\n}"}],"structuredContent":{"result":"{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"user_id\": \"user\",\n  \"flowise_url\": \"http://openagentic-api:8000/api/flowise-workspace\",\n  \"status\": \"healthy\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-02-21T00:34:49.483590\"\n}"},"isError":false},"status":"completed","startTime":1771634089276,"endTime":1771634090911,"duration":1635,"timestamp":"2026-02-21T00:34:50.911Z"},{"id":"toolu_bdrk_01XypucpFiF5gMNEqGFWd4y2","name":"flowise_list_chatflows","tool":"flowise_list_chatflows","toolName":"flowise_list_chatflows","serverId":"openagentic_flowise","serverName":"openagentic_flowise","executedOn":"mcp-proxy","arguments":{"userId":"user"},"result":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"error\": true,\n  \"status_code\": 401,\n  \"message\": \